OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly fine, with variable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud and some sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Easterly winds will gradually
OL,8,Fstrengthen through the day, leading to
OL,9,Fa cooler feel, especially along
OL,10,FEnglish Channel coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly cloudy with some
OL,13,Fcoastal showers in the south. The
OL,14,Fnortheasterly wind will increase,
OL,15,Fbecoming breezy especially along the
OL,16,Fcoast. Feeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
