OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA cloudy but dry start to
OL,6,FSunday, with brighter spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping during the afternoon but
OL,8,Ffeeling cooler, in the strengthen
OL,9,Fnortheasterly wind.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FMonday, rain band clears south,
OL,13,Ffollowed by brighter spells. Cloudier
OL,14,FTuesday with outbreaks of rain.
OL,15,FWednesday starts off dry with heavy
OL,16,Fshowers developing later.
